    • update

      public void update()
      Updates the simulation and moves the simulation forward by one second. The new burn rate, fuel amount, balloon temperature, velocity, and altitude are calculated in this order. [[The equations used to help calculate the velocity can be found in hw1-2024-spring-2.pdf in Canvas]]
